latestPosts.caption:
Tequila Komos has expanded its footprint in Gurugram after a remarkable performance in Delhi and Goa.

With its thriving nightlife, elite social circles and discerning palates, Gurugram is the perfect destination for the next phase of Komos’ journey. The Gurugram launch was celebrated with a grand event at Lair, bringing together the city’s most influential personalities. The evening featured an exclusive tasting experience, allowing guests to savour the refined complexity of Komos Reposado Rosa, Añejo Cristalino and Añejo Reserva.
